    <briefdescription>
<para>动画组件 </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>继承 Behavior，由 <ref refid="class_shit_1_1_behavior_system" kindref="compound">BehaviorSystem</ref> 每帧调用 onUpdate 推进当前动画时间， 并把当前帧的源矩形 (SDL_FRect) 回写到同 <ref refid="class_shit_1_1_game_object" kindref="compound">GameObject</ref> 上的 SpriteRenderer。</para>
<para>典型用法（三点式 sprite-sheet）： <ref refid="class_shit_1_1_sprite_sheet" kindref="compound">Shit::SpriteSheet</ref> sheet(4, 8, 32, 32); // 4行8列，每帧32×32 auto* anim = go-&gt;addComponent&lt;AnimationComponent&gt;(); anim-&gt;play(&quot;walk&quot;, sheet, {0,1,2,3,4,5}, 0.1f, true); // 全局帧索引数组</para>
<para>或手工添加已构造好的 Animation： anim-&gt;addAnimation(&quot;walk&quot;, std::move(walkAnim)); anim-&gt;play(&quot;walk&quot;); </para>
    </detaileddescription>
